  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      to evaluate the efficacy of a single intravitreal bevacizumab (IVB) injection, 0.1mL (2.5mg),
      against panretinal photocoagulation (PRP)-induced macular thickening and visual disturbance
      in patients with severe nonproliferative diabetic retinopathy (NPDR) and proliferative
      diabetic retinopathy (PDR) and good vision
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
